{"tid":2403541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"831銅鑼灣暴動案 警遭質疑虛構掟汽油彈情節 初五裁定案件是否表證成立","createTime":"2021-02-11T06:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T09:03:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fefef592bd32906a0641af5233ef9c0e1d9c4b8b","tid":2403541,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"前年8.31市民自發到港島各區「行街」，及後演變為警民衝突，16名於銅鑼灣及灣仔一帶被捕的人士事後被控暴動罪，其中15人早前已先後受審。餘下19歲男學生的案件今在區域法院續審。辯方盤問聲稱受汽油彈襲撃的警員時指，片段未見顯示包括被告在內的人投擲汽油彈，地上亦無火光，質疑警員蓄意誣衊被告。<br />\n<br />\n警員11067蕭小虎昨供稱，當日為速龍小隊成員，掃蕩期間在軒尼詩道電車路軌附近受示威者汽油彈襲擊，遂向前追捕，追至中國銀行外，發現包括被告在內的四人，其中兩人各自向他投擲一枚燃燒中的汽油彈。他今在盤問下補充指，四人當時一字排開站立，兩人投擲汽油彈後，四人轉身逃走。<br />\n<br />\n辯方大律師石書銘盤問時引用片段指，在蕭聲稱第二次被汽油彈襲擊的時間，地上並無火光，蕭表示同意。石隨即質疑：「但你話有兩個人向你投擲燃燒緊嘅汽油彈喎，但地上冇火光喎？」蕭解釋，因為汽油彈落在他左後方，而非前方。<br />\n<br />\n石詢問當時四人中有多少人戴頭盔、頭盔又是甚麼顏色，蕭謂：「大部份戴黃色頭盔。」石追問有多少人戴黃頭盔，蕭表示不肯定，並解釋當時注意力集中在汽油彈，故沒有留意，未能準確作答數目。石聞言質疑：「你話當時佢哋背住你，又話佢哋著黑色衫，頭盔顏色係唯一識認，你有乜理由唔留意？」<br />\n<br />\n石再引用呈堂截圖指，被告經過電車站後，左手低垂拿着白色膠袋，右手則撐着傘，問蕭在眾人一字排開時有否看見此情況，蕭稱當時沒有留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/EK66ZHRLDBAEBPRAP2K3HT5XLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FEK66ZHRLDBAEBPRAP2K3HT5XLI%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=f45e8a99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FEK66ZHRLDBAEBPRAP2K3HT5XLI%2F&h=8c51de5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/EK66ZHRLDBAEBPRAP2K3HT5XLI/</a>"},{"pid":"5ded5ad7b4611b60617052abb452ea4c7aeb0630","tid":2403541,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"手足歸隊！藍絲條恥笑do not split不割蓆入Oscar條片竟然仲高views過正身<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2403533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2403533</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"60277b9c38c19296c2221207db5372524fdad336","tid":2403541,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"小心港共之後都會上訴"},{"pid":"8c4428d87cc601a59ecbdaa7edb978b2962a2fc0","tid":2403541,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60277b9c38c19296c2221207db5372524fdad336","tid":2403541,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"小心港共之後都會上訴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"唔洗小心 係一定會上訴"},{"pid":"532eeaf7bb3fa38f5495228129c53dae2323f68e","tid":2403541,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4428d87cc601a59ecbdaa7edb978b2962a2fc0","tid":2403541,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60277b9c38c19296c2221207db5372524fdad336","tid":2403541,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"小心港共之後都會上訴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"唔洗小心 係一定會上訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"yes.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a612f58aeb152b7288d1a7d8ce2483206211ba50","tid":2403541,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a40fb1f6f45e0cb761db4e59c967845f21abeae","tid":2403541,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf300d5cfac16bdae461f29de90c783074d21e2a","tid":2403541,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /